# isPresented

**Instance Property**

A binding controlling if the find navigator is presented, or nil if no binding has been provided via the [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/View/findNavigator(isPresented:)] modifier.

## Declaration

```swift
var isPresented: Binding<Bool>?
```
